WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 28]

02:38.910 --> 02:39.600
You Chi.

02:44.910 --> 02:45.560
You Chi?

03:04.700 --> 03:05.390
Wu Shiguang,

03:06.330 --> 03:07.350
ever since we were kids,

03:08.660 --> 03:09.220
I've been

03:09.220 --> 03:10.350
your little tagalong.

03:12.750 --> 03:13.560
I was your playmate.

03:15.160 --> 03:16.470
I left home with you

03:17.750 --> 03:18.970
and braved danger with you.

03:22.750 --> 03:23.680
Why can't I remember it?

03:24.000 --> 03:26.760
I even followed you to the Shilin Sect.

03:27.950 --> 03:29.060
Have you seen Wu Shiguang?

03:29.540 --> 03:30.420
I've got something really fun

03:30.420 --> 03:31.040
to tell him.

03:31.330 --> 03:32.390
Master Dragon Deity?

03:32.700 --> 03:33.680
He's busy.

03:33.790 --> 03:34.850
Don't bother him.

03:35.160 --> 03:36.600
He's still got a lot to deal with.

03:43.370 --> 03:45.810
The people at the Shilin Sect are all pretty nice.

03:46.200 --> 03:47.310
You little weasel,

03:47.580 --> 03:49.010
keep that Shilin Sect token on tight.

03:49.330 --> 03:50.560
Or you'll be wiped out.

03:54.080 --> 03:56.100
But the Shilin Sect isn't my home.

03:57.370 --> 03:58.330
A weasel demon like me

03:58.330 --> 03:59.060
shouldn't be here.

04:00.950 --> 04:02.180
Is that the Dragon Deity?

04:02.580 --> 04:03.680
- Look. - He has to be.

04:03.700 --> 04:04.510
Even the demon hunter commander

04:04.580 --> 04:05.560
is standing behind him.

04:05.580 --> 04:07.430
- He has to be. - That's right.

04:07.580 --> 04:09.430
Exactly, he must be the Dragon Deity!

04:10.290 --> 04:11.060
Being here,

04:11.830 --> 04:12.830
I feel like I'm in a skin

04:12.830 --> 04:13.930
that doesn't belong to me.

04:15.040 --> 04:15.720
It's uncomfortable.

04:20.200 --> 04:20.890
Now you've got

04:21.080 --> 04:22.640
so many demon hunters

04:22.790 --> 04:23.470
following you.

04:24.910 --> 04:25.560
Maybe

04:26.080 --> 04:27.810
you don't really need me anymore.

04:39.250 --> 04:40.140
I need to talk to you.

04:40.540 --> 04:41.640
Commander Li wants to see me.

04:41.910 --> 04:42.890
Let's talk later.

04:51.020 --> 04:57.580
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

04:57.980 --> 05:04.340
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

05:05.780 --> 05:12.300
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

05:12.740 --> 05:18.460
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

05:20.140 --> 05:25.860
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

05:26.700 --> 05:27.390
So

05:28.870 --> 05:29.430
I'm leaving,

05:29.790 --> 05:30.390
Wu Shiguang.

05:36.370 --> 05:37.350
You idiot weasel.

06:02.160 --> 06:03.010
Formless Moon,

06:03.910 --> 06:04.640
hear my command.

06:08.950 --> 06:09.680
Go.

06:11.000 --> 06:12.470
Activate the Nuwa Formation

06:13.750 --> 06:15.970
and reveal the Four Pillars

06:16.950 --> 06:17.810
that uphold the earth.

06:18.700 --> 06:19.850
Yes.

06:41.700 --> 06:42.680
Have you seen You Chi?

06:51.330 --> 06:51.930
Wangyan!

06:52.330 --> 06:52.930
Canyue.

06:55.000 --> 06:55.720
Canyue!

06:57.120 --> 06:57.970
Canyue.

06:59.950 --> 07:00.680
Stop her.

07:03.040 --> 07:03.720
Canyue.

07:19.410 --> 07:19.970
Wangyan,

07:21.950 --> 07:23.180
what happened?

07:25.250 --> 07:26.010
Jiu Ying...

07:32.000 --> 07:33.430
Jiu Ying isn't dead.

07:38.870 --> 07:41.260
He possessed Wuyi.

07:48.500 --> 07:49.470
Do you remember

07:49.950 --> 07:50.760
the four divine trees

07:50.830 --> 07:52.600
that uphold the earth I told you about?

07:53.000 --> 07:54.850
The Tree of Water grew beneath the sea.

07:55.250 --> 07:56.350
Its trunk

07:56.700 --> 07:58.930
is now the throne in Formless Moon's main hall.

08:02.950 --> 08:03.680
Go.

08:04.500 --> 08:05.430
Yes.

08:09.330 --> 08:10.430
The Crying Elm,

08:10.450 --> 08:12.560
now reduced to a broken stump,

08:13.200 --> 08:14.890
is the Tree of Earth.

08:27.620 --> 08:28.680
The Firefluff Tree hidden

08:28.700 --> 08:30.100
in the axle of Wei mansion's weaving workshop

08:30.370 --> 08:31.430
is the Tree of Fire.

08:44.450 --> 08:45.220
Why does Jiu Ying

08:45.250 --> 08:46.100
want to destroy

08:46.500 --> 08:47.350
the Four Pillars?

08:47.950 --> 08:49.680
He wants the earth to collapse,

08:49.910 --> 08:51.220
all living things to perish,

08:52.120 --> 08:53.260
and this world

08:54.540 --> 08:56.720
to be left with nothing but fear and despair.

08:58.080 --> 08:59.600
Where is the Tree of Metal?

09:03.410 --> 09:05.100
The Shilin Sect's Golden Scale Tree

09:07.040 --> 09:08.100
is the Tree of Metal.

09:09.450 --> 09:09.890
Good thing

09:10.160 --> 09:11.640
there is the Eternal Formation

09:12.250 --> 09:13.180
keeping them away.

09:13.700 --> 09:14.180
No.

09:17.250 --> 09:18.100
Wuyi

09:19.660 --> 09:21.260
has a Shilin Sect token.

09:53.510 --> 09:54.890
Wu Shiguang, why haven't you come to find me?

09:56.580 --> 09:57.310
If you don't

09:57.790 --> 09:58.460
show up today,

09:58.460 --> 09:59.470
I won't be so easy

10:00.250 --> 10:01.060
to cheer up!

10:15.750 --> 10:16.350
Ye Changsheng,

10:16.950 --> 10:17.970
bring the nearby townsfolk

10:18.370 --> 10:19.410
into the Shilin Sect

10:19.410 --> 10:19.990
for protection.

10:19.990 --> 10:20.560
Yes.

10:23.290 --> 10:23.850
Hurry!

10:25.290 --> 10:26.140
Watch your step!

10:29.660 --> 10:30.470
This way!

10:30.660 --> 10:31.260
Quick!

10:34.150 --> 10:34.890
Keep up!

10:39.120 --> 10:39.680
Be careful!

10:39.750 --> 10:40.430
- Hurry! - Go!

10:43.380 --> 10:43.850
Move!

10:44.330 --> 10:45.010
- Go! - Keep up!

10:45.010 --> 10:45.510
Inside!

10:45.580 --> 10:46.140
Go!

10:56.250 --> 10:58.220
If the Four Pillars collapse completely,

10:59.910 --> 11:02.220
heaven and earth, including the Shilin Sect,

11:02.370 --> 11:03.470
will topple.

11:03.700 --> 11:04.970
We have to stop Jiu Ying,

11:05.950 --> 11:06.600
but...

11:08.790 --> 11:09.560
Master Dragon Deity.

11:11.060 --> 11:15.660
♪In this world of black and white, there's always one flower blooming bright♪

11:15.900 --> 11:20.260
♪The weak may bow, but someone always steps ahead♪

11:20.620 --> 11:25.020
♪As the moon shifts, blade-like scales cry out with gleaming edge...♪

11:27.620 --> 11:30.100
My soul I devote. Long live the dragon.

11:30.140 --> 11:34.980
♪We swear to cut down every demon and every fiend...♪

11:37.500 --> 11:38.350
Master Dragon Deity,

11:39.250 --> 11:40.100
we await your orders.

11:40.100 --> 11:44.380
♪We take life and death in stride, with no fear and no sorrow♪

11:44.420 --> 11:47.980
♪We raise our bowls to the sky, hot blood burning, cold tears gleaming♪

11:48.000 --> 11:49.140
Members of the Formless Moon

11:49.330 --> 11:51.470
can draw on the elemental power of the Four Pillars.

11:52.080 --> 11:52.950
The possessed sisters

11:52.950 --> 11:54.200
will be much stronger

11:54.200 --> 11:55.060
and hard to defeat.

11:57.040 --> 11:58.260
Only spells that counter

11:58.270 --> 11:59.390
the pillars' elements

11:59.450 --> 12:00.560
can oppose them.

12:01.040 --> 12:01.850
Mo Yuntan,

12:02.200 --> 12:03.760
your artifact, the Spirit Brush,

12:03.870 --> 12:04.680
uses ink-based

12:05.040 --> 12:06.100
water magic.

12:06.750 --> 12:07.560
It can counter fire.

12:09.540 --> 12:10.640
Leave the Firefluff Tree to me.

12:16.910 --> 12:17.660
The Crying Elm

12:17.660 --> 12:19.260
is the oldest tree,

12:20.040 --> 12:21.350
the ancestor of all trees.

12:42.330 --> 12:44.010
My artifact, Golden Resonance,

12:44.370 --> 12:45.140
counters wood.

12:45.540 --> 12:46.100
Perfect.

12:54.000 --> 12:55.930
My blade is a divine weapon left behind by a mountain demon.

12:56.540 --> 12:57.930
For centuries, it'd drawn on

12:58.370 --> 13:00.510
the essence of the soil from the peak of Mount Nandang.

13:00.830 --> 13:01.720
Earth counters water.

13:02.000 --> 13:03.760
I'll handle the Formless Moon's Tree of Water.

13:11.540 --> 13:13.010
That leaves the Golden Scale Tree.

13:15.370 --> 13:16.060
Hua Qi...

14:13.080 --> 14:13.890
What,

14:14.950 --> 14:16.470
are you going to attack your sister?

14:17.290 --> 14:19.220
It's Jiu Ying I'm going to strike at.

14:21.330 --> 14:22.560
Give my sister back!

14:57.870 --> 14:58.470
What happened?

15:00.540 --> 15:01.350
You Chi,

15:02.750 --> 15:03.560
leave.

15:03.620 --> 15:04.220
No way.

15:04.870 --> 15:05.330
How can I leave

15:05.330 --> 15:06.140
when you're like this?

15:07.120 --> 15:07.680
Hua Qi,

15:07.910 --> 15:08.850
I'm no healer.

15:09.080 --> 15:10.220
Is there any way I can help?

15:11.200 --> 15:11.640
Yes.

15:12.580 --> 15:13.260
Take my place

15:14.290 --> 15:15.140
and save the Golden Scale Tree.

15:16.660 --> 15:18.260
Save the Golden Scale Tree?

15:18.620 --> 15:19.260
How?

15:20.250 --> 15:20.680
Should I

15:21.500 --> 15:22.600
catch bugs or water it?

15:39.790 --> 15:40.430
Always

15:40.870 --> 15:41.930
keep this token on you.

15:42.290 --> 15:43.060
Otherwise,

15:43.120 --> 15:44.010
the ancient formations

15:44.040 --> 15:45.310
all over the Shilin Sect

15:45.580 --> 15:47.890
will reduce you to ashes in an instant.

15:55.000 --> 15:55.930
Remember:

15:56.910 --> 15:58.640
no matter what you are

15:59.000 --> 16:00.140
or how capable you are,

16:01.000 --> 16:02.510
always give it everything you've got

16:02.910 --> 16:04.310
and do your best.

16:05.450 --> 16:06.810
Only then can you have no regrets.

16:16.200 --> 16:17.640
A little weasel

16:17.950 --> 16:19.810
thinks he can fight a nine-tailed fox?

16:24.450 --> 16:25.180
Haven't you heard?

16:26.910 --> 16:27.510
Fire counters metal.

16:29.450 --> 16:30.180
Hua Qi,

16:31.620 --> 16:33.390
you're draining your power.

16:34.080 --> 16:34.760
Almost done,

16:35.120 --> 16:35.890
Master Dragon Deity.

16:37.290 --> 16:38.310
Hold on a little longer.

16:49.000 --> 16:49.560
Wangyan!

16:58.250 --> 16:59.010
Wangyan,

17:00.330 --> 17:02.060
did you think

17:02.660 --> 17:03.850
I couldn't beat you?

17:53.080 --> 17:53.890
Shiguang,

17:54.950 --> 17:56.390
you are the only one in this world

17:56.660 --> 17:57.810
I still can't let go of.

17:58.830 --> 17:59.930
Though I am gone,

18:00.790 --> 18:02.060
the Star Stone remains.

18:03.040 --> 18:04.350
If you find yourself in dire straits one day,

18:05.040 --> 18:06.350
it may yet help you once.

18:07.500 --> 18:08.390
But remember this.

18:09.370 --> 18:10.970
The Star Stone's power is too great.

18:11.910 --> 18:12.890
Do not use it rashly.

18:13.040 --> 18:13.720
Master...

18:15.330 --> 18:16.220
"Heaven and earth tremble.

18:16.660 --> 18:17.510
Chaos fills the world.

18:18.120 --> 18:19.640
An old soul returns against time.

18:20.200 --> 18:21.810
A new moon reshapes the world."

18:22.500 --> 18:23.310
"Heaven and earth tremble.

18:24.700 --> 18:25.760
Chaos fills the world."

18:26.910 --> 18:28.970
The last share of Chi Wen's Dragon Deity's Power

18:29.950 --> 18:31.180
took Ji Ling's heart stone

18:31.700 --> 18:32.970
to the Dragon Abyss.

18:34.000 --> 18:35.600
Perhaps thousands of years from now,

18:36.200 --> 18:37.600
it may take human form.

18:38.580 --> 18:39.930
"An old soul returns against time."

18:42.250 --> 18:43.220
"An old soul returns against time."

18:44.040 --> 18:44.640
Hua Qi.

18:47.830 --> 18:48.600
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

18:54.200 --> 18:55.010
Give me your hand.

18:59.450 --> 19:00.310
Go to the Dragon Abyss.

19:00.700 --> 19:01.680
Use my blood to activate

19:02.000 --> 19:03.060
the Star Stone illusion

19:03.450 --> 19:04.560
and bring Ji Ling's

19:05.000 --> 19:05.760
heart stone inside.

19:06.540 --> 19:07.220
Go, now.

19:07.660 --> 19:08.310
All right.

19:08.380 --> 19:10.500
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

19:10.580 --> 19:15.700
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

19:16.020 --> 19:18.220
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

19:18.340 --> 19:23.140
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

19:23.620 --> 19:25.740
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

19:25.780 --> 19:30.660
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies...♪

19:31.450 --> 19:32.140
This...

19:32.870 --> 19:34.140
isn't my limit yet.

19:34.420 --> 19:39.980
♪Let's gaze above♪

19:41.790 --> 19:43.100
Do my best

19:45.000 --> 19:46.220
and leave no regrets!

19:51.000 --> 19:52.640
You only know fire counters metal.

19:53.620 --> 19:54.600
But do you know

19:54.950 --> 19:57.260
that ice counters fire?

20:10.580 --> 20:12.700
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

20:12.780 --> 20:17.900
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

20:18.220 --> 20:20.420
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

20:20.540 --> 20:25.340
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

20:25.820 --> 20:27.940
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

20:27.980 --> 20:32.860
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

20:33.140 --> 20:36.380
♪Stay with me♪

20:36.620 --> 20:41.020
♪Let's gaze above♪

20:41.020 --> 20:43.060
♪It's your light, your storms♪

20:43.100 --> 20:48.140
♪Your watchful eyes, that set the night alight♪

20:48.260 --> 20:51.540
♪And lead me♪

20:51.740 --> 20:56.620
♪Sailing afar♪

21:28.000 --> 21:29.220
A fleeting moment in the mortal world

21:29.870 --> 21:30.930
is a thousand years in the illusion.

21:31.790 --> 21:32.810
Master Dragon Deity,

21:33.830 --> 21:35.180
I will bring Ji Ling back.

21:45.450 --> 21:46.260
Your weapon's gone,

21:47.160 --> 21:48.260
and you still won't give up?

21:48.830 --> 21:49.640
The blade's gone,

21:51.450 --> 21:52.510
but I'm still here.

21:52.700 --> 21:54.560
Today, I am going to defeat you!

22:08.620 --> 22:09.390
Who says

22:10.500 --> 22:11.260
a weasel

22:12.540 --> 22:13.930
can't beat a nine-tailed fox?

22:27.910 --> 22:28.680
Wu Shiguang,

22:31.040 --> 22:31.850
this time,

22:34.120 --> 22:34.640
I...

22:34.950 --> 22:36.060
I didn't

22:38.040 --> 22:39.180
hold you back.

22:47.700 --> 22:48.640
You'd better not

22:50.200 --> 22:51.140
lock me

22:51.450 --> 22:53.100
inside the Cosmic Pouch again.

24:16.620 --> 24:22.260
♪Clad in golden scales, I gaze from the valley high♪

24:22.700 --> 24:28.860
♪Wiping away the dark to let the moonlight shine♪

24:29.300 --> 24:30.700
♪Through all joys and sorrows♪

24:30.860 --> 24:32.420
♪Bitter and sweet♪

24:32.620 --> 24:35.780
♪The moon stays by my side♪

24:36.220 --> 24:42.020
♪Its light is my most precious scale♪

24:49.100 --> 24:54.620
♪The moon accompanies me as I roam the mortal world♪

25:01.860 --> 25:09.380
♪She looks at me and says, you're not alone tonight♪

25:23.120 --> 25:23.680
"An old soul..."

25:26.740 --> 25:27.450
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

25:27.450 --> 25:28.160
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

25:28.160 --> 25:29.140
[An old soul returns against time.]
"Returns against time."

25:29.140 --> 25:29.780
[A new moon reshapes the world.]

25:32.870 --> 25:33.640
You're back.

25:34.830 --> 25:35.680
I am.

25:37.410 --> 25:38.140
And

25:39.950 --> 25:40.890
so are they.

25:53.060 --> 25:58.980
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow...♪

26:04.750 --> 26:05.470
Master.

26:07.140 --> 26:13.020
♪I truly miss the taste of your tears♪

26:13.300 --> 26:13.900
♪So please♪

26:14.180 --> 26:19.780
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

26:20.380 --> 26:20.980
♪So please♪

26:21.260 --> 26:26.020
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun♪

26:26.040 --> 26:27.220
Why are you all back?

26:28.370 --> 26:30.180
Because Ji Ling has already awakened the people

26:30.910 --> 26:31.760
of the Formless Moon.

26:34.000 --> 26:34.760
Wake.

26:40.060 --> 26:45.220
♪Asking the night why it keeps me bound♪

26:47.380 --> 26:54.380
♪Has anyone heard my call?♪

26:54.620 --> 26:59.700
♪Like a feather waiting for its final fall♪

27:00.500 --> 27:06.580
♪I would buy osmanthus and wine again, but I'm no longer young♪

27:07.420 --> 27:13.380
♪A speck of dust weighs heavy on my heart and throat♪

27:14.260 --> 27:21.300
♪I pace back and forth, counting footprints, too afraid to look up♪

27:21.420 --> 27:27.740
♪Trapped like rainwater in a lake♪

27:27.780 --> 27:34.300
♪So many dawns and dusks in pouring rain♪

27:34.660 --> 27:37.260
♪Twilight weighs down beyond our sight♪

27:37.260 --> 27:41.140
♪Trapping us small souls so tight♪

27:41.660 --> 27:48.980
♪So many lives, like a speck of dust♪

27:49.380 --> 27:55.620
♪Yet every tiny me speaks loud and just♪

28:30.540 --> 28:30.930
Wang,

28:32.330 --> 28:34.250
the Four Pillars have been corrupted

28:34.250 --> 28:35.810
by the evil energy inside Jiu Ying.

28:37.580 --> 28:38.420
Only by sacrificing

28:38.420 --> 28:40.180
the Formless Moon power within us

28:41.250 --> 28:43.220
can we cleanse that evil energy.

28:44.120 --> 28:45.890
The wrong was ours.

28:46.950 --> 28:48.680
Let us make amends ourselves.

28:49.620 --> 28:50.220
Wang,

28:50.830 --> 28:51.430
we leave

28:51.950 --> 28:52.760
the rest to you.

28:54.000 --> 28:54.890
Save this world

28:55.500 --> 28:57.430
we have guarded for a millennium.

29:02.000 --> 29:02.560
What is it?

29:03.910 --> 29:04.930
What did the Moon Summoning Pearl say?

29:06.580 --> 29:07.140
Nothing.

29:08.160 --> 29:09.850
The sisters have all come to their senses.

29:12.290 --> 29:13.760
They're repairing the Four Pillars.

29:17.700 --> 29:18.810
The collapse has stopped.

29:20.830 --> 29:22.260
Looks like they're all restored.

29:56.080 --> 29:57.310
I'll check on the Golden Scale Tree.

29:57.620 --> 29:58.430
Be careful.

29:59.540 --> 30:00.310
I've got it covered here.

30:26.790 --> 30:28.560
You're still alive?

30:29.620 --> 30:30.680
Too bad Lu Wuyi thought

30:30.950 --> 30:32.350
you were truly dead.

30:32.620 --> 30:33.930
She was so heartbroken

30:35.120 --> 30:36.510
that even her soul

30:36.540 --> 30:38.060
scattered into nothing.

30:39.160 --> 30:39.850
Jiu Ying,

30:41.160 --> 30:42.310
you killed Wu.

30:44.330 --> 30:45.100
Today,

30:46.080 --> 30:48.600
I will make sure your soul is utterly destroyed.

31:02.290 --> 31:03.180
Lu Wuyi,

31:04.580 --> 31:06.470
you woke up again?

31:06.750 --> 31:07.760
I told you,

31:09.540 --> 31:10.890
the one who should get out

31:12.370 --> 31:13.390
is you.

31:17.080 --> 31:17.640
Wu.

31:21.620 --> 31:22.640
Ji,

31:23.950 --> 31:26.510
Jiu Ying has been trying to take control.

31:27.620 --> 31:28.600
Ji,

31:29.700 --> 31:30.560
do it.

31:31.700 --> 31:32.680
Kill me.

31:38.120 --> 31:40.260
Since I was created, I've been controlled

31:41.450 --> 31:42.390
my whole life.

31:44.700 --> 31:45.970
This time,

31:48.000 --> 31:50.010
I want to be my true self.

31:52.620 --> 31:53.470
Help me,

31:55.330 --> 31:56.220
Ji.

32:12.540 --> 32:13.140
Form up.

32:16.620 --> 32:17.510
Qisha of the Southern Dipper.

32:17.620 --> 32:18.430
Tiantong of the Southern Dipper.

32:18.580 --> 32:19.260
Pojun of the Northern Dipper.

32:19.910 --> 32:20.470
In positions!

32:34.580 --> 32:39.060
♪In this world of black and white, there's always one flower blooming bright♪

32:39.300 --> 32:43.660
♪The weak may bow, but someone always steps ahead♪

32:44.020 --> 32:48.420
♪As the moon shifts, blade-like scales cry out with gleaming edge♪

32:48.820 --> 32:53.020
♪A vow of double flowers, to guard tomorrow together♪

32:53.020 --> 32:54.980
♪Moon and scales shine in radiant splendor♪

32:55.180 --> 32:57.540
♪As the winds rise, dragons and foxes cry in strife♪

32:57.580 --> 33:01.980
♪At the world's end, the destined soul rides proud and free♪

33:02.540 --> 33:04.820
♪Soaring high on the wind♪

33:04.980 --> 33:07.140
♪I will gather the stars and cradle the moon for you♪

33:07.300 --> 33:08.820
♪Bearing treasured fragments of wonder♪

33:08.940 --> 33:12.780
♪Behold the moon and scales in radiant splendor♪

33:14.420 --> 33:17.180
♪There's always one flower blooming bright♪

33:17.420 --> 33:21.780
♪The weak may bow, but someone always steps ahead♪

33:22.140 --> 33:26.540
♪As the moon shifts, blade-like scales cry out with gleaming edge♪

33:26.940 --> 33:31.580
♪A vow of double flowers, to guard tomorrow together♪

34:42.620 --> 34:43.310
Master.

35:08.330 --> 35:08.910
You Chi.

35:09.860 --> 35:10.540
Wangyan,

35:11.410 --> 35:12.310
I did great

35:13.870 --> 35:14.760
this time.

35:17.160 --> 35:17.890
She said

35:18.790 --> 35:19.390
a weasel

35:20.750 --> 35:22.060
couldn't beat a nine-tailed fox,

35:22.870 --> 35:23.560
but

35:24.120 --> 35:24.890
look,

35:26.330 --> 35:27.890
I still beat her.

35:32.660 --> 35:34.180
I helped, didn't I?

35:35.330 --> 35:36.100
Oh, right.

35:36.750 --> 35:37.470
Look.

35:38.370 --> 35:39.260
I was

35:41.080 --> 35:42.140
so smart this time.

35:44.750 --> 35:45.640
Wu Shiguang

35:46.080 --> 35:47.100
won't get to call me

35:47.120 --> 35:48.180
an idiot again.

35:49.910 --> 35:50.810
Do you know?

35:51.620 --> 35:52.350
Wu Shiguang

35:52.870 --> 35:53.890
always says

35:54.330 --> 35:55.760
that when danger comes,

35:57.830 --> 35:59.890
I'm the type to dig a hole and hide in it.

36:00.580 --> 36:01.850
Before you came,

36:03.000 --> 36:04.350
I was so sad,

36:05.750 --> 36:07.850
because I was going to die here alone,

36:09.700 --> 36:11.100
and no one would ever know.

36:12.660 --> 36:13.810
Wu Shiguang

36:14.620 --> 36:16.310
must think I ran away again.

36:20.060 --> 36:20.510
Oh,

36:20.540 --> 36:21.310
right.

36:21.950 --> 36:23.810
Remember to tell him

36:24.450 --> 36:25.220
that I...

36:27.000 --> 36:27.850
I really...

36:30.120 --> 36:32.180
really did my best.

36:32.700 --> 36:33.510
I did...

36:34.830 --> 36:36.560
I did my best.

36:40.250 --> 36:41.100
You Chi.

36:41.370 --> 36:42.010
You Chi!

36:42.900 --> 36:46.780
♪And through the winter cold, it stayed with me♪

36:49.060 --> 36:55.580
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

36:55.900 --> 37:02.300
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

37:03.780 --> 37:10.260
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

37:10.660 --> 37:16.220
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

37:18.540 --> 37:25.020
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

37:25.500 --> 37:31.380
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

38:24.410 --> 38:25.140
How?

38:26.000 --> 38:28.350
Lu Wuyi's soul was unusually resilient.

38:29.160 --> 38:30.240
I was never able to find

38:30.240 --> 38:31.760
a way to erase it completely.

38:32.120 --> 38:33.310
I should thank you,

38:33.500 --> 38:34.350
Wu Shiguang.

38:35.000 --> 38:36.470
With your Dragon Deity's Power,

38:37.250 --> 38:38.290
you wiped out

38:38.290 --> 38:40.100
the last trace of her soul

38:41.160 --> 38:43.430
and let me own this body completely.

38:46.950 --> 38:49.220
Why won't Lu Wuyi's body die?

38:52.380 --> 38:53.100
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

38:53.100 --> 38:53.820
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

38:53.820 --> 38:55.100
[An old soul returns against time. A new moon reshapes the world.]

38:57.120 --> 38:58.510
The Oracle Stone is missing a piece.

38:59.000 --> 38:59.890
The Oracle Stone!

39:00.540 --> 39:01.390
Besides a fragment

39:01.660 --> 39:03.430
of Jiu Ying's spirit,

39:03.950 --> 39:05.760
a fragment of the Oracle Stone is in her too.

39:08.120 --> 39:09.310
Wu's body

39:09.540 --> 39:12.060
was made from the flesh and blood of nine-tailed foxes.

39:12.910 --> 39:14.090
It has the power of rebirth

39:14.090 --> 39:15.720
granted by the Formless Moon.

39:16.750 --> 39:18.670
If she also has the Oracle Stone's

39:18.670 --> 39:20.010
ever-living divine power,

39:21.200 --> 39:21.720
then...

39:27.200 --> 39:28.640
Is there really no other way?

39:31.500 --> 39:32.760
"An old soul returns against time.

39:34.660 --> 39:35.970
A new moon reshapes the world."

39:40.000 --> 39:40.720
A new moon...

39:52.700 --> 39:53.930
There is still one way.

39:56.830 --> 39:57.850
And it's the only way.

40:02.000 --> 40:02.970
You've thought of it too.

40:04.620 --> 40:05.390
What is it?

40:08.790 --> 40:09.890
Turn back time

40:10.830 --> 40:11.930
and go back to the past

40:13.910 --> 40:15.720
to stop Lu Wuyi from ever being born.

40:16.830 --> 40:17.640
In other words,

40:19.450 --> 40:21.640
erase Lu Wuyi's existence completely.

40:27.580 --> 40:29.310
Didn't Lonescale tell you?

40:30.660 --> 40:33.350
The recent past of a few days can be changed.

40:34.750 --> 40:37.060
But Lu Wuyi was born 50 years ago.

40:38.290 --> 40:40.560
To go back that far

40:40.950 --> 40:42.100
and change the past?

40:44.330 --> 40:45.430
A fool's dream.

40:47.660 --> 40:49.010
"A new moon reshapes the world."

40:50.040 --> 40:51.060
Since the Oracle Stone

40:51.370 --> 40:53.060
gave such a prophecy,

40:53.950 --> 40:54.930
it means

40:58.040 --> 40:59.560
this is destined to happen.

41:02.830 --> 41:04.390
I was a fallen star from beyond the heavens.

41:05.950 --> 41:07.720
I'm not bound by the laws of this world.

41:11.580 --> 41:12.930
There was one question

41:14.000 --> 41:15.470
I spent my whole life pondering.

41:16.790 --> 41:18.220
Even after bitter years of cultivation,

41:18.830 --> 41:20.060
I could never solve it.

41:21.290 --> 41:23.350
You bear extraordinary power from beyond the heavens.

41:23.750 --> 41:24.470
Slaughter

41:24.910 --> 41:26.680
is not your only choice.

41:27.700 --> 41:29.010
I hope that one day,

41:29.500 --> 41:31.970
you'll find the true meaning of coming to this world

41:32.330 --> 41:33.760
after crossing

41:34.410 --> 41:35.600
countless galaxies.

41:36.790 --> 41:37.600
For the past thousand years,

41:37.660 --> 41:38.760
I have asked myself

41:41.040 --> 41:43.180
why I came to this world

41:44.830 --> 41:45.560
and what

41:47.870 --> 41:49.720
I could do for it.

41:51.290 --> 41:52.720
Now I understand.

41:54.620 --> 41:56.100
After I crossed the galaxies

41:56.700 --> 41:57.970
and came to this world,

41:59.290 --> 42:00.510
I brought disaster upon it

42:01.290 --> 42:02.510
and gave rise to Jiu Ying.

42:07.120 --> 42:08.100
So

42:09.750 --> 42:11.640
it should be me who brings him to an end

42:13.090 --> 42:14.620
and saves this world.

42:31.540 --> 42:32.700
♪It's your light♪

42:32.900 --> 42:34.780
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

42:34.940 --> 42:38.060
♪That set the night alight♪

42:38.420 --> 42:44.940
♪And lead me through the fight♪

42:46.700 --> 42:48.580
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

42:49.020 --> 42:53.460
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

42:54.260 --> 42:55.940
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

42:56.100 --> 43:01.500
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

43:02.260 --> 43:07.660
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

43:09.980 --> 43:16.020
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

43:16.980 --> 43:19.140
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

43:19.420 --> 43:24.260
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

43:24.620 --> 43:26.940
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

43:27.140 --> 43:32.220
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

43:32.460 --> 43:34.460
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

43:34.740 --> 43:39.100
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

43:40.100 --> 43:47.060
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

44:03.620 --> 44:06.580
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

44:07.660 --> 44:11.060
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

44:11.860 --> 44:14.380
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

44:14.620 --> 44:17.700
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

44:18.100 --> 44:20.420
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

44:20.940 --> 44:25.340
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

44:25.580 --> 44:27.740
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

44:28.140 --> 44:33.100
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

44:33.340 --> 44:34.500
♪It's your light♪

44:34.700 --> 44:36.540
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

44:36.740 --> 44:39.860
♪That set the night alight♪

44:40.620 --> 44:50.060
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
